doctype html
html
  head
    title Link Expired
    style.
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #333333;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        height: 100vh;
      }
      .container {
        text-align: center;
        max-width: 500px;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 28px;
        color: #4152b3;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #555555;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      ul {
        text-align: left;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 0 20px;
        color: #555555;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #4152b3;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: color 0.3s ease;
      }
      .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #ffffff;
        background-color: #4152b3;
        padding: 12px 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: bold;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }
      .btn:hover {
        background-color: #2c3a8c;
      }
  body
    .container
      h1 Link Expired
      p Unfortunately, the link you clicked has expired. Email verification links are time-sensitive and expire for your security.
      p Here's what you can do next:
      ul
        li Double-check that you used the most recent email verification link we sent you.
        li If you can't find the email, check your spam or junk folder.
        li If the link has expired, don't worry! You can request a new verification email.
